{"tid":1509441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[前排發夢話你知] 向後跑而有手足被拉係咩一回事","createTime":"2019-08-27T00:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T07:10:45.000Z","uid":33797,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"261638f2e4a338c0756e9441e0c0307416d59d0a","tid":1509441,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:08:46.000Z","msg":"我見到好多人都怪手足點解掉頭走唔救人，又點解做唔到背對撤退。等我呢個發夢做過前線講下d真實情況，希望你地諗都點拆個問題<br />\n<br />\n(雖然我有戰術點拆，但我唔係大台指揮唔到人)<br />\n<br />\n前線背對撤退時，通常都會有後面一個拉一個背囊退，向呢個時候，班發爛渣會響收近咗同示威者嘅距離之後，會突然向前衝，撲向示威者<br />\n<br />\n首先造成個效果係，正面撤退嘅第一二排會驚被撲倒，而希望加速背對退，但中後排係睇唔到到第一二排有呢個需要，所以冇加到速<br />\n<br />\n之後會發生嘅事係，發爛渣響衝埋嚟果陣，會有隻出胡椒去攻擊拉住第一排嘅第二三排手足，令佢地再拉唔住第一排，同時其他發爛渣會用棍去攻擊第一二排準備拘捕。響佢地又大力，又有助跑之下，好易撲倒第一排，甚至第二排拘捕  (加上手足背對撤退，發爛渣即使向前用盾撞第一排，都好易令第一排手足失重心而仆街，繼而造成局部嘅骨牌效應)<br />\n<br />\n呢個嘅撲到成功，加上第二三排受到攻擊之後，造成嘅恐慌會更大，之後就會有人轉身向後跑，同時會叫人走啊<br />\n<br />\n呢個動作唔一定第二排之後嘅人發起，第一排嘅人都會咁。當你見到同你平排嘅手足被撲到，會feel到下一個好可能會係自己，你就會轉身叫人走<br />\n<br />\n之後成件事係，中排嘅人會因為前面有人叫 走啊就跟住轉身向後跑，當中會有手足轉唔切身而被撞到跌倒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以背對撤退，一定要要還擊   (好似第一排有盾有棍去攻防，第二排有長竹去守第一排，第三排見發爛渣衝就遠攻，第四排以後要傳嘢俾第三排掉)  去保住第一二排嘅安全，只係一個拉一個退，作用唔大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家仲有咩好建議保到前排，希望可以分享下"},{"pid":"9239b0f2fbeca977cf4081c4cd9a278a04a7c8fd","tid":1509441,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=5d48eb35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=3448be99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=c348535c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d7b091fadcdefc8c11964c1d7dfe6e57614eb906","tid":1509441,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:11:36.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"a141fd1584cc06b6a2cd8589b31910d4492abed0","tid":1509441,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:13:24.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"13a19d27a66ec168b088bb5419d3eb4799858fb7","tid":1509441,"uid":151667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:14:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a34132a57a7b0ad573ae7f24c3834a078346b90","tid":1509441,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:14:29.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"7ac6c8957ccff0a6f22501762b1801f6c990d476","tid":1509441,"uid":268217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:14:38.000Z","msg":"葉劉訪問蒙大拿州大進讒言，竟抹黑香港示威者，阻止《香港人權及民主法案》通過。以下是當事美國議員的twitter，請大家盡量班師入去留言，澄清這些立法會議員並不代表我，促請美國國會盡快通過法案，制裁香港反民主的一干人等。<br />\n<br />\nSteve Daines<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/stevedaines\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fstevedaines&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=d72b96c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/stevedaines</a><br />\n<br />\nJon Tester<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/senatortester\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fsenatortester&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=5e2b3c21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/senatortester</a><br />\n<br />\nGreg Gianforte<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://