ok.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=0931eed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=cd365143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102458676557543%2Fposts%2F1582783125191750%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=ed9634f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo</a><br />\n將窗嗌口號變成一種普及的生活方式，會好大感染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyn9vh9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcyn9vh9.png&h=f1d434e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb6e0e88d04441b45d20d2d6f6c40ec99dd5f3a7","tid":1509441,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66726db2e482b24d6beaf37e691f54f1c11a9f2e","tid":1509441,"uid":19821,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:19:08.000Z","msg":"有一樣野好緊要係見到佢地開始衝 就要遠攻 <br />\n平時企到遠一遠遠攻會tk 但如果速龍衝入射程範圍 遠攻用火魔法令佢地退後應該會有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:27:21.000Z","msg":"我上面都有講，但第五排開始都唔好遠攻，傳俾第四第三排做好d，咁會冇咁易tk<br />\n<br />\n背對撤退(有拉背囊果種)唔適合用火魔法  (除咗第一排，或者路邊游擊手)，事關用之前要點火，好似燒到附近手足<br />\n<br />\n但要用一定要成個第一排都用，如果唔係班發爛渣會集火拉第一排有掉果個"},{"pid":"86cae95f4aa557064f1711db307cd999eb461742","tid":1509441,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6bcf59453a1ee8902894886ea5bc30a49aaacfb","tid":1509441,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82a70a9a772fba1a1c5a83e6ab82c38e495a1727","tid":1509441,"uid":33797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a968d14963dd8830d24ba3ba631cca698c3a12f9","tid":1509441,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:16:07.000Z","msg":"727都係咁做 我第二排拎棍扑落差佬 拉返個差d落單既手足<br />\n所以第二排同第一排應該用棍 竹去同狗拉距離"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:19:50.000Z","msg":"根本就係要咁做，保到前排，撤退就唔會做成恐慌，就唔會有咁多手足被拉<br />\n<br />\nBTW多謝巴打救咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:26:03.000Z","msg":"同埋走佬先落波子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:29:50.000Z","msg":"波子會跟地形look走，好d嘅方法係第三排同你掉d磚頭上去卡住班發爛渣，仲可以做到擊退呢個效果添"},{"pid":"437bb67b785326b023638e336419556dca70e200","tid":1509441,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:32:14.000Z","msg":"係前排企既時候唔好正面企<br />\n打斜啲個人 唔好正面面對狗<br />\n事關斜腳去做進或退都可以好方便<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解每一次都係我地做防<br />\n無幾可係主動進攻/counter attack<br />\n如果打counter attack<br />\n狗上前既時候先搵第三排用魔法阻止狗推前或者突進<br />\n然後如果仲上前既話 一二排巴打就可以進攻<br />\n打一個措手不及<br />\n利申 上過最前線 真心對撚住狗個下個心唔多唔少都淆底仔 前排唔夠疊馬會好撚容易奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d3a1707b4d34ef18afcd9c4c751e76a9cb2889","tid":1509441,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:34:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad51cf73064fe121dccb6a754fd320dccc9dd4e2","tid":1509441,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86cae95f4aa557064f1711db307cd999eb461742","tid":1509441,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6bcf59453a1ee8902894886ea5bc30a49aaacfb","tid":1509441,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82a70a9a772fba1a1c5a83e6ab82c38e495a1727","tid":1509441,"uid":33797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:19:50.000Z","msg":